    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902860/extras/8ad6ea107a6f774a5ad1776be52e067f.poster.avif?t=1770767665\" width=780 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902860/extras/8ad6ea107a6f774a5ad1776be52e067f.webm?t=1770767665\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902860/extras/8ad6ea107a6f774a5ad1776be52e067f.mp4?t=1770767665\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>当光芒熄灭时，留下的将会是什么？</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当宇宙被阴影侵蚀，你将化身为最后一缕光明——「微光」。黑暗愈发浓重之际，追随那微弱闪烁的光辉，抵达最后的星球。被温暖所吸引，你踏上了为宇宙夺回光明的旅程。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902860/extras/c6923fce06a9c98d08e9762d9fef1d6b.poster.avif?t=1770767665\" width=780 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902860/extras/c6923fce06a9c98d08e9762d9fef1d6b.webm?t=1770767665\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902860/extras/c6923fce06a9c98d08e9762d9fef1d6b.mp4?t=1770767665\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <strong>为宇宙存亡而战</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >高耸的巨像挡在你与目标之间。这些冷酷的毁灭巨像，会不择手段熄灭你逐渐暗淡的光芒。对他们而言，你从未该存在，只是必须被纠正的错误。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902860/extras/6c4c487af29af7cb1caf4d5291602ee0.poster.avif?t=1770767665\" width=780 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902860/extras/6c4c487af29af7cb1caf4d5291602ee0.webm?t=1770767665\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902860/extras/6c4c487af29af7cb1caf4d5291602ee0.mp4?t=1770767665\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>进化的战斗，无尽的挑战</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >类魂风格 BOSS 连战游戏《光之传说：奥德赛》，通过三阶段的致命战斗来击败巨像，每一步都更加严酷。新的攻击、全新的模式，以及愈发紧张的压迫感不断袭来。要战胜寂静中步步逼近的黑暗，你必须学习、磨炼，并在每个瞬间作出适应。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902860/extras/fc2e5d18660672cc8eb808278ff5d394.poster.avif?t=1770767665\" width=780 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902860/extras/fc2e5d18660672cc8eb808278ff5d394.webm?t=1770767665\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902860/extras/fc2e5d18660672cc8eb808278ff5d394.mp4?t=1770767665\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>揭开失落世界的秘密</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在战斗的间隙，探索早已湮没的文明废墟吧！解开古老谜题，破译遗落信息，揭示巨像的真正起源。随着发现的累积，你将愈发沉浸于那曾经被光辉照耀的世界历史，以及守护光芒所付出的沉重代价。</p>",
